       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ALTER-TEST.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-AMOUNT        PIC S9(7)V99.
       01  WS-RATE           PIC S9(3)V9(4).
       01  WS-RESULT         PIC S9(9)V99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-LOGIC.
           MOVE 5000.00 TO WS-AMOUNT.
           MOVE 0.0375  TO WS-RATE.
           ALTER CALC-DISPATCH TO PROCEED TO CALC-COMPOUND.
           PERFORM CALC-DISPATCH.
           STOP RUN.

       CALC-DISPATCH.
           GO TO CALC-SIMPLE.

       CALC-SIMPLE.
           COMPUTE WS-RESULT = WS-AMOUNT * WS-RATE.

       CALC-COMPOUND.
           COMPUTE WS-RESULT = WS-AMOUNT * (1 + WS-RATE).
